{"tid":1301090,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"視點31 -- 【黑鏡人生‧淪落失信人】","createTime":"2019-07-09T14:16:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T14:21:46.000Z","uid":240362,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"eac2107795a48255b5245cc528a47042b7507027","tid":1301090,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T14:16:00.000Z","msg":"中國過去十年建構全國社會信用體系，收集得來的生活數據，用來評價民眾誠信。<br />\n據最新公布，全國已有近1400萬人被評為失信，社會上寸步難行；內地多以「老賴」形容他們，除了欠債不還老賴賬，「失信人」何以失信、遭遇如何？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=srcGtNTMWvs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsrcGtNTMWvs&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBHyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=8deecc59\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=srcGtNTMWvs</a>"},{"pid":"2059df2bed19f552743f8733c43dd40144d0eac6","tid":1301090,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T14:17:20.000Z","msg":"【中國式‧信用】<br />\n「守信者，一路暢行；失信者，寸步難行」。<br />\n<br />\n近年中國各地政府推行社會信用評級，要求各部門以至企業，向中央平台集中推送個人或企業的「守信」和「失信」資料，建立「紅名單」及「黑名單」，再加以聯合獎懲。預計2020年，這套全國社會信用系統將基本建設完成，並應用在14億中國人的生活當中。<br />\n<br />\n《視點31》訪問了十年前率先推行信用評分系統的江蘇徐州睢寧縣，了解政策背後的目的和實際操作。當國家機構負起判斷民眾誠信高低之責，會利用甚麼樣的標準、尺度衡量？一個人或企業的信用狀況，對他的生活有何影響？社會是否變得更有誠信，還是變成一個全面監控的「奧威爾式」制度？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sPZ9gSIffjE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DsPZ9gSIffjE&d=aELkmJ%2FgRhSQUMA2B8lhBHyU4AarvyINc8S1qmu5ZLM%3D&h=7f79806d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=sPZ9gSIffjE</a>"},{"pid":"a839618553d196fd09c31eaf7f62a55cec669ce3","tid":1301090,"uid":94290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T14:21:46.000Z","msg":"唔好意思阻阻你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n7月10即係聽日截止喇！<br />\n填咗嘅就幫手推！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【DQ區選反對確認書】同我入黎填撚左佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1297868\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1297868</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hJy9Juz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhJy9Juz.png&h=f48d8803&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入去推上熱門呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}